    {
      "id": 17676,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "The REQUEST_URI was assigned as the value of a hidden field in the login form without proper escaping resulting in a reflected cross-site scripting bug. Browsers were mitigating the issue and IE was only impacted if XSS protection was disabled. We've improved the sanitization of this field.",
